                <p>I had a deeper look on the issue, it might be that you don&#8217;t have the right permissions on the Pi. In the terminal on the Raspberry Pi, do this for all the files of the tutorial:</p>
<p>chmod 777 name_of_the_file</p>
<p>It should solve the problems.</p>
