                <p>I was wondering how you chose the Transistor. I need to turn on a 12v circuit. Do you know if i&#8217;d need a different transistor?</p>
                                <a class='comment-reply-link' href='/control-a-relay-from-anywhere-using-the-raspberry-pi/?replytocom=8398#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm("comment-8398", "8398", "respond", "387")'>Reply</a>                </div>
